message.content:
I'm not sure specifically what you are asking for, but here are 10 acronyms related to military organizations and operations:

1. NATO - North Atlantic Treaty Organization
2. UN - United Nations
3. EU - European Union (not exclusively a military organization but has some security initiatives)
4. AFSOC - Air Force Special Operations Command
5. CENTCOM – United States Central Command
6. NSA – National Security Agency 
7. NORAD – North American Aerospace Defense Command 
8. SOF – Special Operations Forces 
9.CIA- Central Intelligence Agency
10.JSOC-Joint Special Operations Command
